<?xml version="1.0"?>
<ScenContainer xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
  <ScenTitle>Gotland</ScenTitle>
  <ScenDescription>&lt;BODY&gt;&lt;H1&gt;OPERATION BALTIC SPEAR&lt;/H1&gt;
&lt;P style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; COLOR: #ffcc00; TEXT-ALIGN: center; LETTER-SPACING: 2px"&gt;CLASSIFIED // SOVIET NAVAL OPERATION &lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Date:&lt;/STRONG&gt; June 1985&lt;BR&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Location:&lt;/STRONG&gt; Gotland, Baltic Sea&lt;BR&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Command:&lt;/STRONG&gt; &lt;SPAN class=ussr&gt;Soviet Naval Command&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;/P&gt;
&lt;DIV class=section&gt;
&lt;H2&gt;SITUATION&lt;/H2&gt;
&lt;DIV class=divider&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;P&gt;The island of Gotland remains under control of &lt;SPAN class=sweden&gt;Swedish defensive forces&lt;/SPAN&gt;, acting as a forward observation and denial point in the Baltic Sea. &lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Capture of Gotland will allow the &lt;SPAN class=ussr&gt;Soviet Union&lt;/SPAN&gt; to dominate regional sea lanes and restrict NATO movement. &lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Enemy resistance is expected to be &lt;SPAN class=sweden&gt;fast, localized, and reactive&lt;/SPAN&gt;. &lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV class=section&gt;
&lt;H2&gt;MISSION&lt;/H2&gt;
&lt;DIV class=divider&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;P class=objective&gt;Conduct a rapid, multi-domain assault and establish a Soviet foothold on Gotland before Swedish forces can fully respond. &lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV class=section&gt;
&lt;H2&gt;EXECUTION&lt;/H2&gt;
&lt;DIV class=divider&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN class=ussr&gt;PHASE 1 – AIR PENETRATION&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Su-24 strike aircraft will advance under MiG-23 escort to suppress defensive positions and force Swedish reaction. &lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN class=ussr&gt;PHASE 2 – NAVAL ADVANCE&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Soviet naval elements will push west toward Gotland. Missile engagement with Swedish patrol forces is expected. &lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN class=ussr&gt;PHASE 3 – AIRBORNE INSERTION&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Mi-8 helicopters will deploy landing forces onto eastern Gotland. This phase determines operational success. &lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV class=section&gt;
&lt;H2&gt;FORCES&lt;/H2&gt;
&lt;DIV class=divider&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN class=ussr&gt;SOVIET FORCES&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Krivak-class frigate (command vessel)&lt;BR&gt;Osa-class missile boats&lt;BR&gt;Ropucha-class landing ships&lt;BR&gt;MiG-23 interceptors&lt;BR&gt;Su-24 strike aircraft&lt;BR&gt;Mi-8 transport helicopters &lt;/P&gt;&lt;BR&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN class=sweden&gt;SWEDISH DEFENSES&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;BR&gt;AJS-37 Viggen fighters&lt;BR&gt;Norrköping-class missile boats&lt;BR&gt;HAWK SAM systems&lt;BR&gt;Bofors 40mm anti-aircraft guns &lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV class=section&gt;
&lt;H2&gt;OBJECTIVES&lt;/H2&gt;
&lt;DIV class=divider&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;P class=objective&gt;PRIMARY OBJECTIVE: LAND ALL MI-8 UNITS [STATUS: PENDING] &lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;SECONDARY: Neutralize Swedish naval and air resistance to ensure uninterrupted landing operations. &lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV class=section&gt;
&lt;H2&gt;THREAT ASSESSMENT&lt;/H2&gt;
&lt;DIV class=divider&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Expect rapid response from &lt;SPAN class=sweden&gt;Swedish air and coastal defense forces&lt;/SPAN&gt;. &lt;/P&gt;
&lt;UL&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;High-speed Viggen intercepts&lt;/LI&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Anti-ship missile engagements&lt;/LI&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Medium-range SAM coverage near Visby&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;
&lt;P class=warning&gt;WARNING: FAILURE TO SECURE AIR SUPERIORITY WILL JEOPARDIZE THE LANDING FORCE &lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;DIV class=section&gt;
&lt;H2&gt;COMMANDER’S INTENT&lt;/H2&gt;
&lt;DIV class=divider&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Speed is critical. The operation must overwhelm Swedish defenses before they can coordinate an effective response. The success of the landing force will determine control of the Baltic battlespace. &lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/BODY&gt;</ScenDescription>
  <Complexity>2</Complexity>
  <Difficulty>2</Difficulty>
  <ScenSetting>Gotland, Sweden</ScenSetting>
